age="75" /> </a></div><div id="et-top-navigation" data-height="125" data-fixed-height="30"><nav id="top-menu-nav"><ul id="top-menu" class="nav"><li id="menu-item-10621" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-home current-menu-item page_item page-item-10610 current_page_item menu-item-10621"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/" aria-current="page">Home</a></li><li id="menu-item-11144" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom current-menu-item current_page_item menu-item-home menu-item-has-children menu-item-11144"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk" aria-current="page">Services</a><ul class="sub-menu"><li id="menu-item-10620" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10620"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/oven-cleaning/">Oven Cleaning</a></li><li id="menu-item-10619" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10619"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/carpet-cleaning/">Carpet Cleaning</a></li><li id="menu-item-11452" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-11452"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/pressure-washing/">Pressure Washing</a></li><li id="menu-item-11304" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-11304"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/domestic-house-cleaning/">Domestic House Cleaning</a></li><li id="menu-item-11317" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-11317"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/office-cleaning/">Office Cleaning</a></li><li id="menu-item-11332" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-11332"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/builders-clean/">Builders Clean</a></li><li id="menu-item-11102" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-11102"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/extreme-cleaning/">Extreme Cleaning</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-item-10618" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10618"><a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/contact-us/">Contact Us</a></li></ul></nav><div id="et_mobile_nav_menu"><div class="mobile_nav closed"> <span class="select_page">Select Page</span> <span class="mobile_menu_bar mobile_menu_bar_toggle"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="et_search_outer"><div class="container et_search_form_container"><form role="search" method="get" class="et-search-form" action="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/"> <input type="search" class="et-search-field" placeholder="Search &hellip;" value="" name="s" title="Search for:" /></form> <span class="et_close_search_field"></span></div></div></header><div id="et-main-area"><div id="main-content"><article id="post-10610" class="post-10610 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry"><div class="entry-content"><div id="et-boc" class="et-boc"><div class="et-l et-l--post"><div class="et_builder_inner_content et_pb_gutters3"><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_0 et_pb_fullwidth_section et_section_regular" ><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_fullwidth_slider_0 et_pb_slider et_pb_slider_no_arrows et_pb_slider_no_pagination et_pb_slider_parallax"><div class="et_pb_slides"><div class="et_pb_slide et_pb_slide_0 et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_slide_with_image et_pb_media_alignment_center et-pb-active-slide" data-slide-id="et_pb_slide_0"><div class="et_pb_container clearfix"><div class="et_pb_slider_container_inner"><div class="et_pb_slide_image"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/wg-content/uploads/2016/06/General-cleaning.jpg" alt="Domestic, Commercial Cleaning" height="auto" width="auto" srcset="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/wg-content/uploads/2016/06/General-cleaning.jpg 2707w, https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/wg-content/uploads/2016/06/General-cleaning-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/wg-content/uploads/2016/06/General-cleaning-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/wg-content/uploads/2016/06/General-cleaning-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/wg-content/uploads/2016/06/General-cleaning-1080x720.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 2707px) 100vw, 2707px" class="wp-image-10851" /></div><div class="et_pb_slide_description"><h2 class="et_pb_slide_title">S.R.D Cleaning Services</h2><div class="et_pb_slide_content"><p>We are the number 1 place to be for all your Domestic and Commercial cleaning needs.</p><p>Why not contact us by email or give us a call so we can provide you with some friendly advice or just a free quote!</p><p>email: <a href="mailto:info@srdcleaning.co.uk"><span style="color: #ffffff;">info@srdcleaning.co.uk</span> </a></p><p>Phone: <a style="color: white;" href="tel:07932914900">07932914900</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_section et_pb_section_1 et_section_regular et_section_transparent" ><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_0"><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_0  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_0  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #2276bf;">Domestic and Commercial cleaning specialists</span></h2><p>S.R.D Cleaning offers services to a range of residential and business clients, both large and small.</p><p>Established since Feb 2016 we have undertaken hundreds of jobs all over Wigan, Bolton, and the North west of England.  We provide all our clients a quality service at great prices.</p><p>Our work includes one-off services and on-going contract work. We obtain most of our business through regular clients and referrals. We are CRB checked for you piece of mind,</p><p>For a fantastic deal, contact us today and we will be happy to answer all your questions and discuss your service requirements.</div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_1  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner">S.R.D Cleaning Services are based in Leigh, Greater Manchester, we have had extensive training by the country&#8217;s leading experts to ensure that every job is as close to perfect as possible, giving you that piece of mind knowing that you’re in good hands.</p><p>We also work on behalf of several cleaning agencies, estate agents, building contractors and councils up and down the country all benefiting from our amazing service&#8217;s.</div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_divider et_pb_divider_0 et_pb_divider_position_ et_pb_space"><div class="et_pb_divider_internal"></div></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_1"><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_2_3 et_pb_column_1  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_2  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #2276bf;">Our Service&#8217;s.</span></h2><p>Some of our services are.</p><p>•Builders Cleaning, we do everything from a mid cleans all the way through to sparkle cleans.</p><p>•Extreme Cleaning, whether its a drug den , hoarder or a void property we clean them all.</p><p>•Spring Cleaning, is your home in need of some love after being stuck in for the winter? give us a call were always happy to help.</p><p>•End of Tenancy Cleaning,  if you&#8217;re moving out or have you had messy tenants, we will ensure your property looks great for when you give the key&#8217;s back.</p><p>•Move in Cleaning, moved in to a home that isn&#8217;t quite up to your standards? be rest assured you&#8217;ve come to the right place.</p><p>•After party Cleaning, whether you have not had time or you&#8217;re just not feeling up to cleaning the mess left behind, we have you covered.</p><p>•Contract Cleaning.</p><p>•Student Accommodation Cleaning.</p><p>•Oven Cleaning (We also do Hobs, extractor fans and BBQ&#8217;s), don&#8217;t want to face your oven? let us do the job everyone hates.</p><p>•Carpet Cleaning (We also do rugs and hall runners), are they starting to look dirty? beginning to smell? give us a call we have the very best equipment to tackle your carpets.</p><p>•Ceramic floor tile and laminate floor cleaning.</p><p>•Office Cleaning.</p><p>•Deep Cleaning, things starting to look a little grubby? give us a shout we give your home or office a through once over. you won&#8217;t be disappointed.</p><p>•Pressure Washing (Drives, patio’s, and footpaths).</p><p>•We also clean Dr surgery&#8217;s Residential blocks and more.</div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_3  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner">visit our Facebook Page <a href="http://www.facebook.com/srdcleaning">www.facebook.com/srdcleaning</a> this contains most of our before and after photos.</p><p>Used our services? why not leave us a review on google to let others know just how amazing our service&#8217;s are. <a href="https://g.page/srdcleaning?share">S.R.D Cleaning Services</a></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_2  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_4  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner">Why not give our page a like:)</div></div><ul class="et_pb_module et_pb_social_media_follow et_pb_social_media_follow_0 clearfix  et_pb_bg_layout_light"><li
