 >Follow</span></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_2"><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_3  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_divider et_pb_divider_1 et_pb_divider_position_bottom et_pb_space"><div class="et_pb_divider_internal"></div></div></div></div><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_3"><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_4  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child"><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_5  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h2><span style="color: #2276bf;">Why Choose Our Cleaning Service?</span></h2><p>We are <strong>Fully Insured</strong> and have had <strong>Extensive Training </strong>and with our experience we are sure to get <strong>Fantastic Results.</strong></p><p>All this at a <strong>Very Competitive Price.</strong></p><p>If you&#8217;re in Greater Manchester or any surrounding areas listed give us a call.</div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_6  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p>Do you need your oven, carpets, a house or office cleaned? Not enough hours in the day? would you like to come home to a nice clean and tidy house? If so then give us a call.</p><p>Why not take a look at some of our Services above.</p><p>Looking for a particular service that is not on the list Please <a href="/contact-us">Contact Us</a>  we are always happy to help.</p></div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_divider et_pb_divider_2 et_pb_divider_position_bottom et_pb_space"><div class="et_pb_divider_internal"></div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_7  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light"><div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p style="text-align: center;">SRD cleaning service&#8217;s offer a professional Domestic and Commercial Cleaning Service to all in <a href="https://www.wigan.gov.uk/index.aspx">Wigan</a>, <a href="http://www.leighgolf.co.uk">Leigh</a>, <a href="http://www.theboltonnews.co.uk">Bolton</a>, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swinton,_Greater_Manchester">Swinton</a>, <a href="http://irlamandcadishead.net/">Irlam</a>, <a href="https://www.greatleverandfarnworthgolfclub.co.uk/">Farnworth</a>, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kearsley">Kearsley</a>, Worsley, <a href="http://www.boothstownbugle.co.uk/">Boothstown</a>, <a href="http://www.newton-le-willows.org.uk/">Newton-le-Willows</a>, <a href="http://www.saintsrlfc.com">St Helens</a>, <a href="http://www.agcm.org.uk/">Astley</a>, <a href="https://www.abelheywood.co.uk">Heywood</a>, <a href="http://www.visitoldham.com/">Oldham</a>, <a href="http://www.visitbury.com">Bury</a>, <a href="http://www.visitlancashire.com/explore/chorley">Chorley</a>, <a href="http://intu.co.uk/traffordcentre">Trafford Park</a>, <a href="http://www.visitmanchester.com">Manchester</a> and all surrounding areas.We May also travel to <a href="http://www.liverpoolfc.com">Liverpool</a>, Bradford, Leeds and <a href="http://www.visitpreston.com">Preston</a>. Please <a href="https://www.srdcleaning.co.uk/contact-us/">contact us</a> for a free quote.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article></div><footer id="main-footer"><div class="container"><div id="footer-widgets" class="clearfix"><div class="footer-widget"><div id="adsensewidget-2" class="fwidget et_pb_widget widget_adsensewidget"><h4 class="title">Adsense</h4><div style="overflow: hidden;"> <script data-ad-client="ca-pub-1401280642775305" async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script> <div class="clearfix"></div></div></div><div id="custom_html-3" class="widget_text fwidget et_pb_widget widget_custom_html"><div class="textwidget custom-html-widget"><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>  <ins class="adsbygoogle"
